\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12521223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3296939\charrsid12799358 Do you remember how much space there was between you?
