\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12521223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3296939\charrsid12799358 Did he continue to do that after he was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7160308 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
