\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11340765 RG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3296939\charrsid12799358 Oh no - we used to have fruit - yes.
