\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12521223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3296939\charrsid12799358 Were you paid in the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11340765 RG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3296939\charrsid12799358 No, Madam.
