Well they used to - er - we - I was training once for nearly twelve months to - er - act - take a part as a King in one of our plays and - er - there was - er - er
 - not much - not for the children - not for the actual children, you know, but I do remember this - er - one occasion.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12521223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3296939\charrsid12799358 Did you belong to any other club organised by the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11340765 RG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3296939\charrsid12799358 No.
