\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11340765 RG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3296939\charrsid12799358 Er - had to say it ourselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12521223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3296939\charrsid12799358 So your parents didn't say it generally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11340765 RG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3296939\charrsid12799358 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12521223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3296939\charrsid12799358 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11340765 RG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3296939\charrsid12799358 Yes, Madam.
