\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11340765 RG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3296939\charrsid12799358 Er - a little - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12521223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3296939\charrsid12799358 Do you know what his views were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11340765 RG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3296939\charrsid12799358 Conservative.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12521223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3296939\charrsid12799358 Have you any idea why he held them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11340765 RG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3296939\charrsid12799358 Well - I think mo
stly it was because the firm he was working for were all Conservatives. And I think years ago people used to look on their lives a little bit different from what we do at the moment and his boss voted Conservative so therefore father thought he'd better. 
I think that was - swayed - final reason.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12521223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3296939\charrsid12799358 Not to be independent?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11340765 RG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3296939\charrsid12799358 Exactly.
